## Summary
Amplitude Data's tracking plan feature allows teams to define, document, and manage events, properties, and sources in a centralized location. The article explains how to create and update tracking plans by adding sources, events, event properties, user properties, and groups, as well as how to collaborate with team members and integrate with developer workflows through Ampli Developer Tools.

